:class ejButton : #._SF._ejWidget
⍝ Description:: Syncfusion Button widget
⍝ Constructor:: [text [type]]
⍝ text - the text/content to appear on the button
⍝ type - one of 'submit' (default), 'reset', or 'button'
⍝ Public Fields::
⍝ Text - the text/content to appear on the button


